        "en": "1.set career object<br>2.understanding self-position<br>3. Understand senior official thinking<br>4. The way of promoted and gain wealth<br>5. transform career strategy<br>6. Improve career capabilities<br>7.Business Presentation Introduction<br>8. Business Presentation Concepts<br>9.Business Presentation Types<br>10. Understanding Presentation Tools"
